EDIT 2: well i got it working the way I wanted... Ty for all the help -.- oh well i learned some things about SCAR. Here is the finished script if anyone wants it.
[code]{ SimpleTalker Program.
1) Change the sentences inside the ' ' on lines 2) Start the script 3) Press F1 for it to type Sentence 1. Press F2 for it to type Sentence 2. Press F3 for it to type Sentence 3.
Made by IP-Drowner (Edited by Nething) in addition to 'thenewguy' and 'exps35' script(s). }
Program SimpleTalker; {.include SRL/SRL.scar}
const Chat1 = 'First sentence here.'; //Replace the sentence with your own. Chat2 = 'Second sentence here.'; //Replace the sentence with your own. Chat3 = 'Third sentence here.'; //Replace the sentence with your own.
procedure Const2Text; begin if(IsFKeyDown(1)) then TypeSend(Chat1); Sleep(71) if(IsFKeyDown(2)) then TypeSend(Chat2); Sleep(69) if(IsFKeyDown(3)) then TypeSend(Chat3); Sleep(62) end;
begin repeat Const2Text; Until(IsFKeyDown(9)) end. [/code]
